title: Error when trying to triangulate using 3D and multianimal
body:

**How to Reproduce the problem** I think it's impossible to reproduce all flows because Google Colab cannot use GUI. So I omitted most part. I'm sorry.
My Code about "right" camera

``` config_path = '/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/PreferenceTest-nelabright-2021-06-06/config.yaml' path1='/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/videos/right_hand_0530_1.mp4' path2='/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/videos/right_hand_0530_2.mp4' path3='/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/videos/right_hand_0530_3.mp4' scorername = deeplabcut.analyze_videos(config_path,[path1, path2, path3], videotype='.mp4') deeplabcut.create_video_with_all_detections(config_path, [path1, path2, path3], scorername) deeplabcut.analyze_videos(config_path,[path1, path2, path3], videotype='.mp4', save_as_csv=True) deeplabcut.convert_detections2tracklets(config_path, [path1, path2, path3], videotype='mp4', shuffle=1, trainingsetindex=0, track_method='ellipse') deeplabcut.filterpredictions(config_path, [path1, path2, path3], videotype='mp4', save_as_csv=True, track_method="ellipse") pickle1 = '/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/videos/right_hand_0530_1DLC_resnet50_PreferenceTestJun6shuffle1_8000_el.pickle' pickle2 = '/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/videos/right_hand_0530_2DLC_resnet50_PreferenceTestJun6shuffle1_8000_el.pickle' pickle3 = '/content/drive/MyDrive/4S/videos/right_hand_0530_3DLC_resnet50_PreferenceTestJun6shuffle1_8000_el.pickle' deeplabcut.refine_training_dataset.convert_raw_tracks_to_h5(config_path, pickle1) deeplabcut.refine_training_dataset.convert_raw_tracks_to_h5(config_path, pickle2) deeplabcut.refine_training_dataset.convert_raw_tracks_to_h5(config_path, pickle3) deeplabcut.plot_trajectories(config_path,[path1, path2, path3],filtered = True, track_method='ellipse') ```
